@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Us - YasirSteel</PageTitle>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="hero" style="min-height: 40vh; padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>About YasirSteel</h1>
            <p>Leading the steel industry with advanced manufacturing solutions and uncompromising quality standards.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Company Overview -->
<section class="page-section section-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Our Company</h2>
                <p>YasirSteel stands as a premier manufacturer of reinforcement steel products, operating one of the most technologically advanced fabrication facilities. Since our establishment, we have been committed to delivering excellence in steel manufacturing and setting new industry standards.</p>
                <p>Our state-of-the-art manufacturing processes, combined with stringent quality control measures, ensure that every product meets the highest international standards. We specialize in providing comprehensive steel solutions for the construction industry.</p>
                <p>Located strategically in the industrial heart of Lahore, our facility spans a substantial area with extensive stockyard capabilities, enabling us to serve major construction projects across Pakistan with reliable delivery schedules and consistent quality.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">2018</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Established Year</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">150,000+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Tons Annual Capacity</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Projects Completed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Expert Team Members</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission & Vision -->
<section class="page-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🎯</div>
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>To provide the highest quality steel products and services that exceed customer expectations while maintaining sustainable manufacturing practices. We are committed to being the preferred partner for construction companies seeking reliable, innovative steel solutions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">👁️</div>
                <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                <p>To be recognized as the leading steel manufacturing company in Pakistan, known for our technological innovation, quality excellence, and contribution to the nation's infrastructure development. We envision a future where YasirSteel products are synonymous with reliability and superior performance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">⚖️</div>
                <h3>Our Values</h3>
                <p>Integrity, Quality, Innovation, and Customer Satisfaction form the cornerstone of our business philosophy. We believe in building long-term relationships through transparency, continuous improvement, and unwavering commitment to excellence in everything we do.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

